  "title": "Warehouse Assistant",
  "description": "<p><strong>Work Day: 4-3-3-4, 7am to 7pm / 7pm to 7am</strong></p><p><strong>Job Responsibilities: </strong></p><p>·       Reporting to the Store supervisor and take responsibility to ensure assignments is completed. </p><p>·       Arrangements of incoming materials and outgoing finished goods.</p><p>·       Ensuring 5S in the store and updates of all stock cards.</p><p>·       Ensure kitting accuracy to support production.</p><p>·       Assist in the delivery of FG and ensuring documentation are inspected before shipment. </p><p>·       Assisting in stock count and ensure discrepancy is reported. </p><p><strong>Requirements: </strong></p><ul><li>Min primary / secondary school</li><li>Minimum 1-2 years of relevant warehouse experience / relevant industries</li></ul>",
